nce-lithuania-polls-cant-be-ruled-out-says-security-chief-2024-03-07/</link><description>立陶宛反情报部门负责人周四表示，由于立陶宛支持台湾，“绝对不能排除”中国干预今年欧盟和北约成员国立陶宛的选举。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:31:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-interference-lithuania-polls-cant-be-ruled-out-says-security-chief-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院委员会一致通过TikTok打击法案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-push-congress-ban-tiktok-or-force-chinese-divestiture-gains-steam-2024-03-07/</link><description>美国众议院能源和商务委员会周四一致通过立法，给予中国字节跳动六个月的时间从短视频应用 TikTok 撤资，否则将面临美国禁令。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-push-congress-ban-tiktok-or-force-chinese-divestiture-gains-steam-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国新疆高级官员称伊斯兰教“中国化”“不可避免”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-official-chinas-xinjiang-says-sinicisation-islam-inevitable-2024-03-07/</link><description>新疆共产党高级官员周四表示，北京被指控侵犯人权的中国西北部穆斯林占多数的地区的伊斯兰教“中国化”是“不可避免的”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:16:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-official-chinas-xinjiang-says-sinicisation-islam-inevitable-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港全速推动新安全法案，称风险“迫在眉睫”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-submit-new-national-security-bill-legislature-this-week-2024-03-07/</link><description>香港政府将于周五向立法机关提交“23条”国家安全法案，可能会进一步镇压这个前英国殖民地的异议，香港领导人李家超呼吁“全速”通过该法案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 09:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-submit-new-national-security-bill-legislature-this-week-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>受到制裁打击的油轮Liteyny Prospect停靠在中国以卸载俄罗斯石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sanctioned-tanker-liteyny-prospect-docks-china-offload-russian-oil-2024-03-07/</link><description>两名知情人士称，受到制裁打击的俄罗斯油轮“Liteyny Prospect”号已停靠在中国黄骅港，卸货70万桶俄罗斯索科尔原油货物，清理了因莫斯科石油制裁而中断的部分积压货物。贸易。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sanctioned-tanker-liteyny-prospect-docks-china-offload-russian-oil-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚总理表示，试图遏制中国只会加剧其不满</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/trying-contain-china-will-only-fuel-its-grievances-says-malaysian-pm-2024-03-07/</link><description>马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣周四在澳大利亚发表讲话时表示，遏制中国崛起的企图只会加剧该国的局势，并在该地区制造不和。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/trying-contain-china-will-only-fuel-its-grievances-says-malaysian-pm-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本表示对中俄更密切的军事关系感到严重关切</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-says-it-is-gravely-concerned-about-closer-military-ties-between-china-2024-03-07/</link><description>日本政府最高发言人周四表示，考虑到日本和该地区的安全，东京对中俄之间更密切的军事合作表示严重关切。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-says-it-is-gravely-concerned-about-closer-military-ties-between-china-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港法官驳回亲民主电台主持人煽动叛乱案上诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</link><description>周四，三名香港高等法院法官驳回了民主活动人士谭德志对其定罪和 40 个月刑期的上诉，其中包括 7 项煽动罪。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>全球需求回升，中国出口超预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-trade-beats-forecasts-signals-global-trade-rebound-2024-03-07/</link><description>中国一月至二月的进出口增长超出预期，表明全球贸易正在出现拐点，这对试图支撑步履蹒跚的经济复苏的政策制定者来说是一个令人鼓舞的信号。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:34:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-trade-beats-forecasts-signals-global-trade-rebound-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国1-2月出口增长7.1%，进口增长3.5%，好于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-exports-rise-71-imports-grow-35-beating-forecasts-2024-03-07/</link><description>海关周四公布的数据显示，1-2月中国出口同比增长7.1%，进口增长3.5%，两项数据均好于预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:14:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-exports-rise-71-imports-grow-35-beating-forecasts-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业集团复星旗下旅游部门表示正在审查业务组合</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-conglomerate-fosuns-tourism-unit-says-reviewing-business-portfolio-2024-03-07/</link><description>复星旅文集团周四表示，正在审查其业务组合，以回应路透社有关其正在探索出售酒店度假村的报道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:09:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-conglomerate-fosuns-tourism-unit-says-reviewing-business-portfolio-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国将向六国旅客提供免签待遇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-offer-visa-free-travel-travellers-six-countries-2024-03-07/</link><description>外交部长王毅周四表示，中国将从3月14日起向瑞士、爱尔兰、匈牙利、奥地利、比利时和卢森堡公民提供免签旅行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-offer-visa-free-travel-travellers-six-countries-2024-03-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>